item.title: About
item.description: As a results-driven Data Analyst with over three years of experience, I bring a unique blend of technical and communication skills to the table. My expertise includes customer research, competitor analysis, and inventory forecasting. I have applied these skills to optimize sales data and customer purchase behavior, resulting in a 30% increase in annual sales. In my previous experience, I was fortunate to be part of the “Palent project”, where I utilized data to promote equity in parenting education and support children in a world of technology disruption.
